# HTML Quotations & Citations

---

Here are some often overlooked, but helpful, HTML tags you can use to improve the markup of your pages:

- `<blockquote>`
- `<q>`
- `<abbr>`
- `<address>`
- `<cite>`
- `<bdo>`

